      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW NEVADA (6) has missed the placings at his last two but was third at this track three back and returns to Bendigo where he tends to run well. Looks suited here and big improvement expected. GREYSYND BONNIE (1) made light work of the tricky draw with a quick early sectional last time clocking 30.49 in a 4.5 lengths win at The Meadows over 525m. One of the leading chances again. ANGELANI (2) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at this track over 500m behind Compare Joe (29.19) in a Grade 5. Should be about the money. BUN QUAKE (5) can sneak into the finish.",
